PR (sdk) - https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/pull/11350
PR (mocha) - https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium-mobile-mocha-suite/pull/210

Test Case - 

{code:java}
var win = Ti.UI.createWindow({
    backgroundColor: '#fff'
});

var btn = Ti.UI.createButton({
    title: 'Trigger'
});

btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
    Ti.API.info('Hello world!');
    Ti.Geolocation.reverseGeocoder('37.773972',  '-122.431297', function(e){
       Ti.API.info('inside  reverse!');
	   Ti.API.info(JSON.stringify(e));
    });
});

win.add(btn);
win.open();
{code}

Build verified. There is now parity between the two platforms.

{code:java}
countryCode
{code}

